husky - commit-msg hook exited with code 1 (error)
reason:
.git/hooks/
pre-commit
    |
    | Husky executes the pre-commit hook
    | Usually runs lint-staged
    | lint-staged runs tools such as Prettier/ESLint
    |
    v
commit-msg
    |
    | Husky executes the commit-msg hook
    | The commit-msg hook calls commitlint
    | commitlint checks the commit message format
    |
    v
Git commit is completed
husky + commitlint requires conventional commits, which format is type(scope): message

